---

<article
  class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 text-gray-300 md:flex-row"
>
  <div
    class="[&>p]:mb-4 [&>p>strong]:text-teal-500 [&>p>strong]:font-normal [&>p>strong]:font-mono text-pretty order-2 md:order-1"
  >
    <p>
      I'm Francisco Rodríguez Ruiz, a Software Engineering student at the
      University of Colima with various skills in many <strong>theoretical and practical</strong> fields.
    </p>

    <p>
      A <strong>young, enthusiastic, capable, and self-taught</strong> person who always strives to give his best in any work he undertakes.
    </p>
    
  </div>

  <img
    width="200"
    height="200"
    src="/img/yoMoto.jpeg"
